sql_result.sql: WITH base AS (SELECT student.real_name, course.course_name, score.term, score.score_value FROM student JOIN score ON student.id = score.student_id JOIN course ON score.course_id = course.id WHERE student.real_name LIKE '孙%' AND student.gender = '男' AND student.is_deleted = 0 AND score.is_deleted = 0 AND course.is_deleted = 0) SELECT base.real_name, base.course_name, base.term, base.score_value FROM base ORDER BY base.real_name, base.course_name, base.term
